Text:
So I guess this means the supply route for our new
commercial facility will proceed as planned, with no
changes.

That's right. We'll implement our current strategy
in addition to our existing plan. This is a realistic,
reasonable, and feasible strategy based on the
documents prepared by Gamma and Epsilon.

...If all goes well, Gamma, this will be a major
turning point for our company's future.

Indeed. It may be fair to say we could use this
strategy as a starting point for building a new
framework!

Gamma, Epsilon, you two prepare to execute this
mission immediately.

Gamma, you also have your company work to deal with,
so Epsilon will lead preparations.
Understood.
Me, lead? Please leave it to me!

Beta, you'll continue to monitor the underground intel
related to the commercial area of the capital.
Understood.

Zeta, keep a close eye on A-Okay Co. Report back any
unusual activity.
Mm...fine.

Eta, you'll continue building the new commercial
facility. Please stick to the schedule—not too early,
not too late.
*yawn* Fine...as annoying as it is...
What am I gonna do?
Delta, you'll work with me on the finishing touches.

You'll be on standby for now, but I promise you a
stage where you can run rampant.
...Fine! I'll wait until it's time to hunt!
Shadow Garden... Commence operation!
Three days before opening Luna, Ltd.'s new facility—
Eeeeek! Baaandits!
Heeeelp!!!
Hey! Wait...!

...Jeez, they sure didn't waste any time fleeing.
Even the horses they've abandoned look stunned...

We were ordered to take out any witnesses, but by
the look of it, they had zero sense of responsibility
for their cargo—I doubt they had any idea who we
were.

...The cargo checks out! They were all destined for
Luna, Ltd. in the capital!
Good! Let's take it to the designated location!

Wonder what's in these things. It wouldn't hurt to
take a peak—

Don't do it. Trust is everything in the mercenary
trade. I'd hate to be treated like a bandit because
you've left traces of tampering with the crates.

That said, this is quite the aggressive move on
A-Okay Co.'s part!

Not sure what Luna, Ltd. did, but they must've
overstepped their bounds.

A-Okay Co. is also conducting attacks on other coaches
belonging to Luna, Ltd. on the road. Come on, let's go!
...Are they gone?

It looks like it. By the way, your acting was
terrible!
Come on! I say we were about the same!

Really? I thought I gave a pretty convincing
performance...
Well done.
Lady Zeta?!
Right! They've robbed the entire shipment, as planned!

I'll cover the rest. You two head back and report
to Alpha.

Here's my written order to you. Don't worry—show this
to Alpha, and she'll know you haven't neglected your
duty.
Are you going to track them personally, Lady Zeta?

I want to confirm for myself that the setup is going
according to plan.
Understood! We'll leave it in your capable hands!

Ohh, Lady Zeta...how're you soooo cool?! I mean,
you're younger than me!

Hey, watch it! You're letting your inner emotions
spill out!
Heh...

...Now then, I wonder where the stolen cargo will end
up.
